This is not meant to be rated ,this is a prefab people will use to help me with my map rating this lacking effort is plain stupid since this is not meant to be pretty,its rough layout for a room see this thread to get more info if you edit in room keep in mind: -the dimension of the room itself cannot be changed. -lights need to be added. -furniture needs to be added. -textures need to be added. -clipping the wals is allowed -custom textures are alowed -custom models are allowed. -credits in the room are allowed if it isnt too big. -advertising is allowed. send the finnished room files to gamingINS@gmail.com or put them in my dropbox.
